=== Slider Widget ===

==== Functionality ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.wizard.SliderWidget
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}
Go back to [[Help:Widgets | Widgets ]]

==== Configuration Settings ====

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.wizard.SliderWidget
}}


==== Example ====

<source>
{{
#widget: Slider
| min = 0
| max = 100
| property = 'sliderValue'
}}
</source>

<img src="../images/help/Slider.png" width="500px" />


In the example above, a new slider is created with which one can select a value in the range between 0 and 100.
If the Slider is used within a Step of a [[Help:WizardWidget | WizardWidget]] upon proceeding to the next step, its value will be saved using "sliderValue" as property.

